=== Festivals ===
* Shishi Shin-go Kito ritual: Feb 11 - Apr 12 (once every 3 years)
** In years of Ox, Dragon, Sheep, and Dog
** First dance on Feb 11; concluding dance in precinct on Apr 12
* Setsubun Festival: day of Setsubun in February
* Kinen-sai / Great purification festival: Feb 21
* Spring annual grand festival
** Spring grand festival: Apr 11 (dedication of Kyoto {{ill|lt=Kongo school|Q11646539|WD=Q11646539|1=Kongō-ryū}} ritual nō "Uzume")
** Kōsha grand festival: Apr 11-12
* Koryujin Shrine grand festival: early May
* Nyudogatake summit Okunomiya spring grand festival: May 12
* Rice-planting festival: last Sunday of May
* Summer purification: Jun 30
* Summer festival: Aug 1
* Autumn annual grand festival
** Eve festival: Oct 10
** Main shrine grand festival: Oct 11
** Betsugu grand festival: Oct 12
* Nyudogatake summit Okunomiya autumn grand festival: Nov 12
* Niiname Festival: Dec 1
* New Year's Eve great purification: Dec 31

