=== Access ===
==== Bus ====
* From {{ill|lt=Yokkaichi Station|Q6414379|WD=Q6414379|lt=Kintetsu Yokkaichi Station|1=Kintetsu Yokkaichi Station}} / {{ill|lt=Yokkaichi Station|Q5358995|WD=Q5358995|lt=JR Yokkaichi Station|1=Yokkaichi Station}}, take {{ill|lt=Mie Kotsu|Q6843516|WD=Q6843516|1=Mie Kotsu}} bus (bound for Tsubaki Grand Shrine), get off at final stop.
* From Kintetsu {{ill|lt=Hiratacho Station|Q5769516|WD=Q5769516|1=Hiratachō Station}} / JR {{ill|lt=Kabase Station|Q5358774|WD=Q5358774|1=Kasado Station}}, take Suzuka community bus (C-BUS, Tsubaki-Hirata line loop), get off at "Tsubaki Ōkamiyashiro" stop.

