* About 5 km from {{ill|lt=Suzuka IC|Q11649468|WD=Q11649468|1=Suzuka interchange}} on the {{ill|lt=Higashi-Meihan Expressway|Q5753692|WD=Q5753692|1=Higashi-Meihan Expressway}}
